doc.after: Jetconnect operates a fleet of 8 Boeing 737-800s registered in New Zealand but in Qantas livery. All Jetconnect aircraft have AVOD (Audio-Visual On Demand) installed, giving passengers access to a wide range of in-flight entertainment options in their seat from gate to gate.
